						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone on the bund of Saṇṇakeṟe.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription commemorates the death of <hi rend="bold">Mallagauḍa</hi> in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Śubhakṛit, Vaiśākha ba. 5.</hi> The village <hi rend="bold">Yātagiri</hi> is mentioned. In the absence of the Śaka year, it is not possible to find out the equivalent of the date. The characters belong to about the <hi rend="bold">15th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
